    "title": "Lead SEO Specialist at Bombay Shaving Company Advisory Limited",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Bombay Shaving Company Advisory Limited. We are on the lookout for a dedicated SEO Specialist to strengthen our Bengaluru-based team.\n\nAbout Bombay Shaving Company Advisory Limited:\nBombay Shaving Company Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bengaluru, Karnataka, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Bombay Shaving Company Advisory Limited!",
